---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 344
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=God the Only Doer
  - 166
By: Richard Rolle
---
Man is not holier or higher for the outward works that he does. Truly
God that is the Beholder of the heart rewards the will more than the
deed. The deeds truly hang on the will, not the will on the deeds.
